   "source": [
    "## Response Spectrum Analysis"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "3db59285",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# define some analysis settings\n",
    "ops.constraints(\"Transformation\")\n",
    "ops.numberer(\"RCM\")\n",
    "ops.system(\"UmfPack\")\n",
    "ops.test(\"NormUnbalance\", 0.0001, 10)\n",
    "ops.algorithm(\"Linear\")\n",
    "ops.integrator(\"LoadControl\", 0.0)\n",
    "ops.analysis(\"Static\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "be1413e6",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "call the eigen Command to extract 7 modes of vibration\n",
    "\n",
    "call the modalProperties Command to generate the report with modal properties"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "08b40a58",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# run the eigenvalue analysis with 7 modes\n",
    "# and obtain the eigenvalues\n",
    "eigs = ops.eigen(\"-genBandArpack\", 7)\n",
    "# currently we use same damping for each mode\n",
    "dmp = [0.05] * len(eigs)\n",
    "# we don't want to scale some modes...\n",
    "scalf = [1.0] * len(eigs)\n",
    "# compute the modal properties\n",
    "modal_props = ops.modalProperties(\"-return\", \"-unorm\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b6d5d500",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Create ODB file to store results;\n",
    "\n",
    "Peform response spectrum analysis"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "a80720d1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",

    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"color: #cf6275; text-decoration-color: #cf6275; font-weight: bold\">OPSTOOL</span> <span style=\"color: #12e193; text-decoration-color: #12e193; font-weight: bold\">::</span>  All responses data with _odb_tag = ResponseSpectrumAnalysis-UX saved in \n",
       "<span style=\"color: #ffc20e; text-decoration-color: #ffc20e; font-weight: bold\">g:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\analysis\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-ResponseSpectrumAnalysis-UX.odb</span>!\n",
       "</pre>\n"
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "\u001b[1;38;2;207;98;117mOPSTOOL\u001b[0m \u001b[1;38;2;18;225;147m::\u001b[0m  All responses data with _odb_tag = ResponseSpectrumAnalysis-UX saved in \n",
       "\u001b[1;38;2;255;194;14mg:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\analysis\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-ResponseSpectrumAnalysis-UX.odb\u001b[0m!\n"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "direction = 1  # excited DOF = Ux\n",
    "ODB = opst.post.CreateODB(\n",
    "    odb_tag=\"ResponseSpectrumAnalysis-UX\",\n",
    "    section_response_dof={\"SectionAggregator\": [\"P\", \"MZ\", \"MY\", \"T\", \"VY\", \"VZ\"]},\n",
    ")\n",
    "for i in range(len(eigs)):  # loop over modes\n",
    "    ops.responseSpectrumAnalysis(direction, \"-Tn\", *Tn, \"-Sa\", *Sa, \"-mode\", i + 1)\n",
    "    ODB.fetch_response_step()\n",
    "# combine the responses by CQC\n",
    "ODB.combine_response_spectrum(method=\"CQC\", lambdas=eigs, damping=dmp, scale=scalf)\n",
    "ODB.save_response()"
   ]
  },
